Package: socialchange
Type: Package
Title: Decompose Social Change into Intraindividual Change and Population Turnover
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Elbers", email = "elbersb@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides methods for decomposing aggregate-level social change
    into components of intraindividual change and population turnover. Population
    turnover includes replacement of individuals (mortality and coming-of-age) and migration.
    Implements event-based, aggregated-data, and simulation-based decomposition
    approaches, as well as classical cohort replacement vs. intraindividual change
    (CR-IC) decompositions and Age-Period-Cohort (APC) models.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
